This mod add a machine, that can combine a diamond sword with legendary stones to make legendary and elementals swords iy's add:
- 4 legendary stones, air, water, fire and thunder
- 4 legendary swords, AirSword that make ennemies levitate to kill them with fall damage, WaterSword to place a source wtaer when ennemie is attacked and right click to add depth striders to your boots, ThunderSword that summon lightning on hit (low durability) and FireSword that launch a FireBall to your ennemies.
- a MultiPotion that is uncraftable for the moment, that with a gui, you can choose effects
- and a fly chesplate (diamond chesplate and fly stone in the combiner) that let you fly in survival when equipped
